Natasha Hadiza Akpoti is a well known politician from Kogi state. She became more popular when she once contested against Yahaya Adoza Bello during a gubernatorial election. In the year 2022, the amazon has trended for good reasons. In this article, I will be looking at three (3) different things that have already made the Kogi politician and philanthropist trend in the present year.
1. Alteration of Political Party: In the early hours of today, several media houses gathered that Natasha Hadiza Akpoti decamped from her former party, the Social Democratic Party (SDP), into the People’s Democratic Party (PDP).
2. Marriage: the second thing that made Natasha Hadiza Akpoti trend in the present year is getting married to Chief Emmanuel Uduaghan from Delta state.
Social media platforms were flocked with her marriage photos when it took place because notable dignitaries like former senate President, Bukola Saraki, Governor Ifeanyi Okowa, Senator Godswill Akpabio, to mention but few, were in attendance.
3. Conferment of Chieftaincy Title: the third time Natasha Hadiza Akpoti trended in 2022 was when the paramount ruler of Ebira land, King Ado Ibrahim, conferred on her a Chieftaincy title. The title is “ohiogu of ebiraland” meaning “the queen of wealth in ebiraland”.
Aside being a politician, Natasha Hadiza Akpoti is also known by many Nigerians to be a philanthropist who helps in lifting the needy out of their situations.



